  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You generate a powerful wind within your palm and send it spiraling outwards towards creatures within a 20-foot cone from you. As your wind travels, it picks up dust, dirt, and other loose debris, making the wind denser. Creatures who are in the affected range must make a Wisdom saving throw, becoming blinded until the end of their next turn on failure or no effects on a success.</p><p>The affected creatures must also make a strength saving throw, being knocked back 30 feet on a failed save. This save is made at disadvantage if they failed their initial save. On a successful save, they are only pushed back 5 feet.</p>",
